Package: buildphylogeny
Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-02-21
Title: Build phylogenies from variant read count matrices.
Authors@R: c(person("LorcÃ¡n", "Pigott-Dix", email = "lp23@sanger.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Tim", "Coorens", email = "tcoorens@broadinstitute.org", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: This package is designed to build a phylogeny from pairs of variant and total read count matrices (mutation X sample). It is a rewrite of https://github.com/TimCoorens/Sequoia, with a focus on readability, reusability, extensibility and efficiency.
License: MIT
